snippet.title: Warhammer Online Developer Discussion #1
snippet.description:
We had the pleasure of meeting with some of the amazing people who worked at Mythic Entertainment on Warhammer Online - Age of Reckoning.

Jeremy Dale - Lead Animator
Kevin Calvert - CSR/Game Designer
Keaven Freeman - Game Designer
Alan Davies - Server Engineer
Mark Davis - Content Director
Vinnie Hatcher - CSR
Mike Stone - Producer
Josh Drescher - Producer
